Detailed Description

Equals to the spirit:model element in the IP-Xact specification.

The Model describes the views, ports and model-related parameters of a component.

References views_.

VLNV Model::getHierRef ( const QString  viewName = QString()  )  const

Get the VLNV of a design in model's view.

This function searches the views of the model for a named view. If view with a given name is not found then invalid vlnv is returned. If the model does not have a hierarchical view then invalid vlnv is returned. If name is not given then the first found design VLNV is returned.

Returns:
A vlnv of a design that is used within this component. Null pointer if design is not found.
